
#Interveiw Questions 
1. Based on this demo, what do you think this product is trying to help you do?
2. How useful does the idea of seeing a full course plan based on your degree feel to you?
3. How valuable is it to know what future courses depend on this course as a prerequisite?
4. How helpful do the course reviews and recommendations seem in helping you choose between options?
5. Is there any information you would expect to see here that is missing from the demo?
